DJ Mediaprint & Logistics Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 31/01/2026 inter alia to consider and approve 1. To consider and approve Un-audited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company for the quarter and nine months ended on December 31 2025; 
2. To consider and approve Material Related Party Transactions of the Company.
3. Any other Business matters if any;
